---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Our Story" activePage="story">

  <div class="story-body">
    <h1 class="story-h">Born Out<br>of Frustration.</h1>

    <p>Every football fan knows the feeling. You finally get your hands on a real Wilson &#x201C;The Duke&#x201D; and it feels nothing like what the pros throw. Stiff leather. Slippery surface. No grip. You spend weeks trying to break it in and it never quite gets there.</p>

    <p><strong>Foley&#x2019;s Footballs started with one simple question: what if you could skip straight to the good part?</strong></p>

    <p>We&#x2019;re a small, registered Pennsylvania business built around one thing &#x2014; taking authentic NFL footballs and professionally conditioning them so you get a game-ready ball from day one. No break-in period. No wasted Sundays. Just the real thing, right out of the box.</p>

    <p>Every ball is sourced directly from the NFL, handled personally, conditioned through a professional multi-step process, inspected by hand, and shipped with care. We started on eBay and built our reputation one throw at a time.</p>

    <p><strong>128 sold. 207 feedback. 100% positive.</strong></p>

    <p>We&#x2019;re just getting started.</p>

    <div style="margin-top: 28px; display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <a href="/store" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; background: var(--gold); color: #0F0A05; padding: 13px 28px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; transition: background 0.15s;">Shop Available Balls</a>
      <a href="/process" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; background: transparent; color: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--faint); padding: 13px 28px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; transition: border-color 0.15s;">The Process &#x2192;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
